WEBVTT

﻿
1
00:01:00.367 --> 00:01:02.825
- Is it a girl?
- Yes.

2
00:01:02.911 --> 00:01:04.618
Show me its arm.

3
00:01:04.705 --> 00:01:07.448
- She bears the mark.
- No!

4
00:01:10.252 --> 00:01:13.791
The omen is true.
I must tell my mother.

5
00:01:16.174 --> 00:01:18.291
- HELP ME!
- I can't.

6
00:01:18.385 --> 00:01:21.173
They're going to kill her.

7
00:01:25.058 --> 00:01:29.018
Please! Please!

8
00:01:29.104 --> 00:01:33.644
Oh. thank you. Ethna. Thank you.

9
00:01:42.200 --> 00:01:44.692
Stand aside for Queen Bavmorda!

10
00:02:09.102 --> 00:02:11.560
You cannot stop the prophecy!

11
00:02:11.647 --> 00:02:14.560
This child will have no power over me.
Start the ritual.

12
00:02:14.650 --> 00:02:19.441
- No. No!
- Where's the baby?

13
00:02:19.571 --> 00:02:21.984
- The midwife.
- Find that baby. Sorsha.

14
00:02:22.074 --> 00:02:25.442
Use the dogs. Bring her back to me alive!

15
00:02:25.535 --> 00:02:27.652
Your reign of terror is at an end!

16
00:02:27.746 --> 00:02:29.729
She will come back.
and she will finish you!

17
00:02:29.815 --> 00:02:31.969
- Silence. wench.
- My baby will finish you!

18
00:02:31.994 --> 00:02:33.278
Kill her.

19
00:06:00.792 --> 00:06:02.784
Dada! Dada!

20
00:06:06.172 --> 00:06:09.461
- Dada! Dada!
- Whoa! Whoa!

21
00:06:10.594 --> 00:06:13.962
Dada! Dada!
We found something in the river.

22
00:06:14.055 --> 00:06:15.967
I can't run off and play
with you now. Ranon.

23
00:06:16.057 --> 00:06:18.299
- I've got work to do.
- You gotta come. Hurry!

24
00:06:23.356 --> 00:06:25.814
Come on.

25
00:06:28.236 --> 00:06:31.274
Don't go near it.
We don't know where it's been.

26
00:06:31.364 --> 00:06:34.198
But. Dada. it's a baby.

27
00:06:34.326 --> 00:06:39.117
- It's not like us.
- No. It's not a Nelwyn.

28
00:06:39.205 --> 00:06:42.744
- It looks like a Daikini baby.
- What's a Daikini?

29
00:06:42.834 --> 00:06:45.167
Daikinis are big.

30
00:06:45.253 --> 00:06:48.371
Giants who live far away.

31
00:06:48.465 --> 00:06:50.673
Oh. she's so cute.

32
00:06:50.800 --> 00:06:53.838
- Can't we keep it. Dada?
- No!

33
00:06:55.221 --> 00:07:00.137
We'll push it downstream and forget
we ever saw it. Come on.

34
00:07:00.226 --> 00:07:02.138
Ufgood! Willow Ufgood!

35
00:07:02.228 --> 00:07:06.438
Shhh! It's the prefect. That's all I need.

36
00:07:06.524 --> 00:07:09.858
Keep it quiet. Don't touch it.

37
00:07:11.529 --> 00:07:15.273
Mr. Burglekutt. my husband
hasn't stolen anything!

38
00:07:15.367 --> 00:07:17.324
Baaa!

39
00:07:20.789 --> 00:07:24.282
Ufgood. you still haven't
paid your debts to me.

40
00:07:24.376 --> 00:07:26.368
Where did you get these seeds?

41
00:07:26.461 --> 00:07:29.169
Well. maybe I used magic.

42
00:07:29.255 --> 00:07:33.215
You're no sorcerer. Ufgood.
You're a clown.

43
00:07:33.301 --> 00:07:36.840
I sell the planting seeds around here.
Now tell me where you got them.

44
00:07:36.930 --> 00:07:40.389
My family's been gathering them
in the forest since last fall.

45
00:07:40.475 --> 00:07:43.468
There's no law against that.

46
00:07:43.561 --> 00:07:47.020
Willow. you didn't leave them
alone by the river?

47
00:07:48.817 --> 00:07:51.150
Magic? You'll need magic...

48
00:07:51.236 --> 00:07:53.723
if you expect to get your planting
done before the rains start.

49
00:07:55.615 --> 00:07:57.527
I will have this land. Ufgood.

50
00:07:57.617 --> 00:08:01.156
And you're gonna end up
working in the mines.

51
00:08:03.373 --> 00:08:07.037
Baaa─

52
00:08:10.213 --> 00:08:13.206
Oh. you're lovely.

53
00:08:13.299 --> 00:08:15.291
Yes. you are.

54
00:08:15.385 --> 00:08:16.921
Kiaya!

55
00:08:17.012 --> 00:08:19.755
Oh. Willow!

56
00:08:19.889 --> 00:08:24.850
- Good girl. Good girl.
- Under no condition whatsoever...

57
00:08:24.936 --> 00:08:27.599
is anyone in this family
to fall in love with that baby.

58
00:08:27.689 --> 00:08:32.400
Yes. you are. Come on. Mims.
Come on. Come on.

59
00:08:32.485 --> 00:08:34.522
There we are. Come on.

60
00:08:34.612 --> 00:08:37.229
Hey. I will not be ignored!

61
00:08:37.323 --> 00:08:41.033
Mims? Ranon?

62
00:08:52.005 --> 00:08:54.122
You're gonna be all clean.

63
00:09:00.805 --> 00:09:04.094
Willow. do you think we should
take her to the village council?

64
00:09:04.184 --> 00:09:06.767
No. No. They'll think it's a bad omen.

65
00:09:06.853 --> 00:09:09.721
There'll be a flood or a drought.
and everyone will blame me for it.

66
00:09:09.814 --> 00:09:12.648
"Willow Ufgood brought around
that Daikini. didn't he?"

67
00:09:12.734 --> 00:09:15.727
"That's right. And he's that
lousy farmer too. Let's get him!"

68
00:09:15.820 --> 00:09:19.905
- Willow. calm down.
- Calm down?

69
00:09:19.991 --> 00:09:22.028
Kiaya. tomorrow's my big day.

70
00:09:22.118 --> 00:09:25.828
Love. the High Aldwin hasn't
picked a new apprentice in years.

71
00:09:25.914 --> 00:09:29.157
Tomorrow's gonna be different.
I just know he's gonna pick me.

72
00:09:31.961 --> 00:09:35.545
- Here. Hold her.
- Hey. no. I don't want her. Kiaya.

73
00:09:35.673 --> 00:09:38.461
- Hold her while I get some milk.
- Oh. no. no. Oh.

74
00:09:46.101 --> 00:09:49.515
Dada. she likes you.

75
00:09:57.987 --> 00:09:59.478
Bye.

76
00:10:01.032 --> 00:10:04.867
Come on. kids. Let's go.

77
00:10:10.875 --> 00:10:14.494
I'll now magically join the rings!

78
00:10:36.442 --> 00:10:39.059
Whoa-ah!

79
00:10:43.908 --> 00:10:46.241
Thank you. son.

80
00:10:46.327 --> 00:10:51.288
If you're easily shocked.
please turn away.

81
00:11:06.514 --> 00:11:08.756
Give me a ripe one. Good.

82
00:11:15.023 --> 00:11:19.484
And now. for my final amazing feat.

83
00:11:19.611 --> 00:11:24.447
I will make this entire pig disappear!

84
00:11:32.498 --> 00:11:37.584
- Mims. see?
- Please. watch very closely.

85
00:11:37.712 --> 00:11:43.299
Wuppity bairn. deru. deru!

86
00:11:45.595 --> 00:11:47.962
- Well─
- What happened to your pig?

87
00:11:50.683 --> 00:11:53.676
No! Hey. come here. you!

88
00:11:58.191 --> 00:12:01.525
I seen enough.

89
00:12:16.709 --> 00:12:18.836
Attention!

90
00:12:18.861 --> 00:12:21.242
The High Aldwin will
now make his choice...

91
00:12:21.346 --> 00:12:23.259
- for his new apprentice!
- You'll be all right.

92
00:12:23.349 --> 00:12:26.508
Bring forth the hopefuls.

93
00:12:26.594 --> 00:12:28.961
- Good luck.
- Good luck. Dada.

94
00:12:29.055 --> 00:12:32.799
Willow Ufgood. a hopeful?
How did he get picked?

95
00:12:32.892 --> 00:12:35.384
Is this a joke?

96
00:12:35.478 --> 00:12:39.939
Willow?

97
00:12:42.277 --> 00:12:47.818
Magic is the bloodstream of the universe!

98
00:12:47.907 --> 00:12:52.447
Forget all you know... or think you know.

99
00:12:52.537 --> 00:12:56.531
All that you require is your intuition.

100
00:12:56.624 --> 00:13:00.789
Now. the power to control the world...

101
00:13:00.878 --> 00:13:04.121
is in which finger?

102
00:13:47.300 --> 00:13:51.840
No apprentice this year!

103
00:14:12.241 --> 00:14:15.609
- Where's Mims?
- I don't know. She was right here!

104
00:14:15.703 --> 00:14:18.571
Take Ranon in there. quick!

105
00:14:26.506 --> 00:14:29.465
Mims!

106
00:14:30.802 --> 00:14:32.964
Mims!

107
00:14:41.229 --> 00:14:45.974
- Mims!
- Dada─

108
00:14:47.318 --> 00:14:50.311
I'm scared. Dada!

109
00:15:00.665 --> 00:15:03.248
Come on!

110
00:15:20.935 --> 00:15:23.894
Vohnkar!

111
00:15:33.406 --> 00:15:36.319
- Check to make sure it's not still alive.
- It's dead!

112
00:15:38.661 --> 00:15:40.368
Dada! Dada!

113
00:15:43.791 --> 00:15:46.033
It was looking for somebody's baby!

114
00:15:49.088 --> 00:15:52.832
- Mommy.
- Kiaya!

115
00:16:00.266 --> 00:16:03.600
Kiaya! Kiaya!

116
00:16:03.686 --> 00:16:06.679
I'm here.

117
00:16:10.776 --> 00:16:14.395
Oh. Kiaya.

118
00:16:14.489 --> 00:16:16.651
We can't keep the baby. Kiaya.

119
00:16:16.741 --> 00:16:19.575
We have to take her
to the village council.

120
00:16:33.090 --> 00:16:38.006
Silence! One beast we can kill.
but there may be more.

121
00:16:38.095 --> 00:16:40.508
And you can be assured
that they won't give up...

122
00:16:40.598 --> 00:16:42.464
until they find what they're looking for!

123
00:16:42.600 --> 00:16:45.843
- It's a sign!
- Who's to blame for this?

124
00:16:45.937 --> 00:16:48.395
We must find the culprit
and throw him in the pit!

125
00:16:48.481 --> 00:16:53.601
In the pit! In the pit!

126
00:16:53.694 --> 00:16:55.811
In the pit! In the pit!

127
00:16:55.905 --> 00:16:59.194
- In the pit! In the pit!
- Willow.

128
00:16:59.283 --> 00:17:03.618
Willow Ufgood.

129
00:17:03.704 --> 00:17:06.162
Come forward.

130
00:17:11.796 --> 00:17:17.087
My children found this baby
alone by the river. High Aldwin.

131
00:17:22.807 --> 00:17:24.924
A Daikini child.

132
00:17:25.017 --> 00:17:28.226
That's what the beasts want.
Let's give it back to them!

133
00:17:28.312 --> 00:17:29.393
Yeah!

134
00:17:29.480 --> 00:17:32.723
- They'll kill her! You can't!
- It isn't one of us.

135
00:17:32.817 --> 00:17:35.480
This child is special!

136
00:17:35.570 --> 00:17:39.860
This child must be taken beyond
the boundaries of our village.

137
00:17:39.949 --> 00:17:42.987
All the way across the great river...

138
00:17:43.077 --> 00:17:45.160
to the Daikini crossroads.

139
00:17:45.246 --> 00:17:49.957
- Well. who'll do that?
- It seems only fair...

140
00:17:50.042 --> 00:17:53.410
that the man to take
this baby to the crossroads...

141
00:17:53.504 --> 00:17:56.338
be the very man who
plucked it out of the river.

142
00:17:58.009 --> 00:18:00.592
I nominate Willow Ufgood.

143
00:18:00.678 --> 00:18:03.261
No!

144
00:18:03.347 --> 00:18:06.806
I will consult the bones!

145
00:18:14.734 --> 00:18:19.729
The bones tell me... nothing.

146
00:18:21.365 --> 00:18:25.234
Do you have any love for this child?

147
00:18:33.711 --> 00:18:38.172
Yes. Yes. I do.

148
00:18:38.299 --> 00:18:42.669
The bones have spoken!

149
00:18:42.762 --> 00:18:46.722
Willow Ufgood. the safety
of this village depends upon you.

150
00:18:46.807 --> 00:18:50.892
- Praise the bones!
- Praise the bones!

151
00:18:50.978 --> 00:18:53.470
But you'll need help.

152
00:18:53.564 --> 00:18:58.855
Who has the courage to protect
our brave fellow on his journey?

153
00:19:00.946 --> 00:19:05.031
- I'll go with him.
- Ah. Meegosh.

154
00:19:05.117 --> 00:19:08.406
- Excellent choice.
- I'll go!

155
00:19:08.496 --> 00:19:10.954
Vohnkar! Vohnkar!

156
00:19:11.040 --> 00:19:13.703
No! Not Vohnkar!
He's the best warrior in the village!

157
00:19:13.793 --> 00:19:16.911
We need him here! Vohnkar. step back!

158
00:19:25.012 --> 00:19:27.595
All this expedition needs is a leader.

159
00:19:27.682 --> 00:19:31.050
And according to the bones.

160
00:19:31.143 --> 00:19:34.102
that leader is...

161
00:19:34.188 --> 00:19:37.022
you. Burglekutt!

162
00:19:37.108 --> 00:19:39.725
Vohnkar!

163
00:19:40.695 --> 00:19:44.780
- What's your problem. son?
- How do you mean?

164
00:19:45.491 --> 00:19:50.156
When I held up my fingers.
what was your first impulse?

165
00:19:50.287 --> 00:19:54.076
- Well. it was stupid.
- Just tell me.

166
00:19:54.208 --> 00:19:58.669
- To pick my own finger.
- Aha! That was the correct answer.

167
00:19:58.754 --> 00:20:03.465
You lack faith in yourself.
More than anyone in the village.

168
00:20:03.551 --> 00:20:06.168
you have the potential
to be a great sorcerer.

169
00:20:06.262 --> 00:20:11.007
Now. when you're out there.
listen to your own heart.

170
00:20:12.810 --> 00:20:15.393
These will protect you.

171
00:20:15.521 --> 00:20:18.059
- Acorns?
- They're magic!

172
00:20:18.149 --> 00:20:22.109
Anything you throw them at
turns to stone.

173
00:20:25.197 --> 00:20:28.440
You have much to learn. young Ufgood.

174
00:20:41.380 --> 00:20:45.841
- Are you scared. Dada?
- No!

175
00:20:45.926 --> 00:20:48.009
Even with fairies in the woods...

176
00:20:48.095 --> 00:20:50.132
that'll put you to sleep
for a hundred years?

177
00:20:51.682 --> 00:20:54.265
- Doesn't bother me.
- Brownies?

178
00:20:54.351 --> 00:20:57.264
- Dragons?
- Trolls?

179
00:20:57.354 --> 00:21:00.813
Trolls that'll skin you alive
and take your face off?

180
00:21:00.900 --> 00:21:04.484
Ranon! You know I hate trolls.

181
00:21:04.570 --> 00:21:07.688
I can be your guard and carry your spear.

182
00:21:07.782 --> 00:21:09.398
Me too. Me too. Dada.

183
00:21:10.951 --> 00:21:16.197
What a lucky father I am.
I wish I could take you bobbins with me.

184
00:21:19.376 --> 00:21:21.914
Good-bye. Dada.

185
00:21:23.964 --> 00:21:26.297
Go play! Go on.

186
00:21:31.931 --> 00:21:34.674
We've never been apart.

187
00:21:37.478 --> 00:21:39.765
I miss you already.

188
00:21:40.898 --> 00:21:44.642
Don't worry. Kiaya. I'll be fine.

189
00:21:44.735 --> 00:21:46.567
I'll be back before you know it.

190
00:21:48.906 --> 00:21:51.569
Well. remember to keep her warm.

191
00:21:53.619 --> 00:21:56.282
And... here.

192
00:21:58.499 --> 00:22:01.287
This will bring you luck.

193
00:22:14.473 --> 00:22:16.760
Good brave people!

194
00:22:18.644 --> 00:22:21.352
The outer world is no place for a Nelwyn.

195
00:22:21.438 --> 00:22:24.101
Give the baby
to the first Daikini you see.

196
00:22:24.191 --> 00:22:26.353
then hurry home.

197
00:22:29.697 --> 00:22:33.281
Tuatha... lokwathrak... tuatha!

198
00:22:33.367 --> 00:22:36.906
Go in the direction
the bird is flying!

199
00:22:40.958 --> 00:22:43.792
It's going back to the village!

200
00:22:45.629 --> 00:22:47.621
Ignore the bird. Follow the river.

201
00:22:47.715 --> 00:22:49.957
Move out!

202
00:23:13.908 --> 00:23:17.401
- Hold on. Meegosh.
- What's wrong?

203
00:23:17.494 --> 00:23:21.454
- We have to stop.
- Stop? Why?

204
00:23:21.540 --> 00:23:23.953
The baby's sick.

205
00:23:28.005 --> 00:23:31.123
She's not sick! Let me see.

206
00:23:32.676 --> 00:23:35.794
Uhaghh! Take her! Take her!

207
00:23:38.474 --> 00:23:41.512
She'll be fine once she gets some rest.

208
00:23:43.896 --> 00:23:45.478
Clean me up.

209
00:23:49.193 --> 00:23:52.402
I didn't ask you
to bring me a dead nursemaid.

210
00:23:52.529 --> 00:23:56.443
- Sorsha. you're useless!
- I'm backtracking the nursemaid's trail.

211
00:23:56.533 --> 00:23:58.695
I'll find where she hid the baby.

212
00:24:00.663 --> 00:24:02.905
Ah. General Kael. at last.

213
00:24:02.998 --> 00:24:07.709
My queen. I have destroyed
the castle at Galladoorn.

214
00:24:07.795 --> 00:24:11.459
Well done. But now I have
another task for you.

215
00:24:11.548 --> 00:24:17.010
Help my daughter to find
that tiny. helpless baby...

216
00:24:17.096 --> 00:24:19.053
that continues somehow to elude her.

217
00:24:21.058 --> 00:24:22.970
The baby of the prophecy?

218
00:24:23.060 --> 00:24:26.474
- The one that would destroy you?
- I need that baby alive.

219
00:24:26.563 --> 00:24:32.480
I must perform the ritual that will exile
the child's spirit into oblivion.

220
00:24:32.569 --> 00:24:35.232
- Find her!
- I don't need his help. Mother.

221
00:24:35.322 --> 00:24:37.359
You'll do as I say. child.

222
00:24:43.831 --> 00:24:45.993
I read the signs.

223
00:24:46.083 --> 00:24:49.247
One day. I fear.
your daughter will betray you.

224
00:24:49.336 --> 00:24:53.501
I trust her loyalty
more than I trust yours.

225
00:25:09.231 --> 00:25:11.769
Move!

226
00:25:11.859 --> 00:25:13.771
Into the bush. Come on. Move!

227
00:25:18.115 --> 00:25:21.825
Come on!

228
00:25:31.462 --> 00:25:34.375
The Nelwyns have got the baby.
We've searched the village.

229
00:25:34.465 --> 00:25:37.378
But a group of them
are on the road somewhere.

230
00:25:37.468 --> 00:25:39.255
They couldn't have gone far!

231
00:25:39.344 --> 00:25:42.303
Widen the search and report to Sorsha!

232
00:25:49.146 --> 00:25:51.433
Come. We'll keep to the woods.

233
00:26:31.188 --> 00:26:35.398
That's it! It's the crossroads!

234
00:26:51.875 --> 00:26:54.709
Keep this fire high.
We don't know what's out there.

235
00:27:00.384 --> 00:27:02.717
What was that?

236
00:27:04.138 --> 00:27:06.881
Get the spears!

237
00:27:23.407 --> 00:27:25.319
Uhh. Uhh.

238
00:27:25.409 --> 00:27:29.244
Give me some water. peck. or you die.

239
00:27:29.329 --> 00:27:31.742
Do you understand?

240
00:27:31.832 --> 00:27:33.698
- Water.
- Yeah.

241
00:27:35.919 --> 00:27:37.785
Hurry up!

242
00:27:41.884 --> 00:27:44.752
Get me some water.
you measly little pecks.

243
00:27:46.138 --> 00:27:48.300
It's a Daikini. We're in luck.

244
00:27:48.390 --> 00:27:50.803
We can't give her to him!

245
00:27:50.934 --> 00:27:54.848
- Somebody put him there for a reason.
- We've got to get rid of her.

246
00:27:54.938 --> 00:27:57.521
- Those soldiers are after us.
- Shhh.

247
00:27:57.608 --> 00:28:00.442
He's looking right at us.

248
00:28:04.448 --> 00:28:06.360
We've got to give that baby to somebody.

249
00:28:06.450 --> 00:28:09.284
I'm somebody.

250
00:28:09.369 --> 00:28:13.659
Let me out of here. I'll take care
of the baby.

251
00:28:15.584 --> 00:28:20.170
- I trust him completely.
- But he tried to strangle me.

252
00:28:20.255 --> 00:28:24.215
- I want to go home!
- No. Burglekutt!

253
00:28:24.301 --> 00:28:27.590
- We should wait!
- Are you challenging my authority?

254
00:28:27.679 --> 00:28:31.013
As far as this baby is concerned. yes.

255
00:28:31.099 --> 00:28:34.137
Don't listen to him. Burglekutt.

256
00:28:35.395 --> 00:28:39.309
Fine. You stay here alone.
but we're going.

257
00:28:39.399 --> 00:28:41.607
That's a bad idea. Very bad.

258
00:28:41.693 --> 00:28:45.061
- Dangerous out there.
- Get the gear. men.

259
00:28:45.197 --> 00:28:48.736
- Vohnkar─
- It's not his decision!

260
00:28:48.825 --> 00:28:52.739
Burglekutt. you're troll dung.

261
00:28:52.829 --> 00:28:54.491
Don't let him talk to you that way.

262
00:28:54.581 --> 00:28:56.664
Listen here. runt.

263
00:28:56.750 --> 00:29:00.710
While you're wasting time here.
your fields aren't getting planted.

264
00:29:00.837 --> 00:29:05.081
- Think about it!
- Burglekutt. I'm gonna─

265
00:29:05.175 --> 00:29:08.543
You're gonna what?

266
00:29:12.516 --> 00:29:15.008
Someday. Burglekutt. Someday.

267
00:29:15.102 --> 00:29:17.059
Vohnkar. let's go!

268
00:29:20.857 --> 00:29:23.520
Meegosh. are you coming?

269
00:29:25.779 --> 00:29:29.363
- I'm staying.
- Come on. men.

270
00:29:29.449 --> 00:29:33.614
Burglekutt. let me out of here.
I'll take care of the baby. I swear.

271
00:29:33.704 --> 00:29:36.367
Just let me out of here. Please!

272
00:29:36.456 --> 00:29:39.949
Vohnkar. let me borrow that spear...
just for a minute.

273
00:29:40.043 --> 00:29:42.285
Well. at least get me some water!

274
00:29:42.379 --> 00:29:47.249
Burglekutt. don't leave me alone
with these two!

275
00:29:47.384 --> 00:29:52.129
What'll we do now. Willow?

276
00:29:52.222 --> 00:29:54.839
Well. that was really stupid. peck.

277
00:29:54.933 --> 00:29:59.724
- Don't call me a peck.
- Oh. I'm sorry... peck.

278
00:29:59.813 --> 00:30:03.557
- Peck. peck. peck. peck.
- You be careful!

279
00:30:03.650 --> 00:30:07.360
I'm a powerful sorcerer. See this acorn?

280
00:30:08.822 --> 00:30:13.317
- I'll throw it and turn you to stone.
- Whoo─

281
00:30:13.410 --> 00:30:15.367
I'm really scared.

282
00:30:15.454 --> 00:30:18.322
No. don't! Don't!

283
00:30:18.415 --> 00:30:21.158
There's a peck here
with an acorn pointed at me!

284
00:30:21.251 --> 00:30:23.914
Oh. I wouldn't want to waste it.

285
00:30:24.004 --> 00:30:27.247
Ha! Peck. peck. peck. peck.

286
00:30:27.341 --> 00:30:29.879
peck. peck. peck. peck. peck!

287
00:30:58.497 --> 00:31:01.331
What was that?

288
00:31:04.795 --> 00:31:08.459
Mornin'. boys.

289
00:31:08.548 --> 00:31:12.667
Rough night last night. wasn't it?

290
00:31:12.761 --> 00:31:16.095
I don't think I introduced
myself yesterday.

291
00:31:16.181 --> 00:31:19.640
My name is Madmartigan.
and you are. uh─

292
00:31:19.726 --> 00:31:22.719
No. Meegosh. Don't go near him.

293
00:31:22.813 --> 00:31:26.147
- He's dangerous.
- I am not.

294
00:31:26.274 --> 00:31:28.357
Good.

295
00:31:33.156 --> 00:31:35.443
Stop! Wait!

296
00:31:37.202 --> 00:31:39.990
Whoa!

297
00:31:45.419 --> 00:31:48.958
- What's going on?
- Smells like a battle.

298
00:31:50.006 --> 00:31:52.544
I suppose you're a warrior.

299
00:31:52.634 --> 00:31:55.126
I am the greatest swordsman
that ever lived.

300
00:31:55.220 --> 00:31:58.008
Hmph.

301
00:31:58.098 --> 00:32:01.808
Say. uh─
Could I have some of that water?

302
00:32:11.570 --> 00:32:16.315
I don't know why I try.

303
00:32:21.121 --> 00:32:24.364
I guess I am gonna die here.
Who cares?

304
00:32:24.458 --> 00:32:26.324
- Here.
- Thanks. friend. Oh!

305
00:32:26.460 --> 00:32:28.827
What's that?

306
00:32:28.920 --> 00:32:32.880
I'd say
two or three hundred horses.

307
00:32:32.966 --> 00:32:36.926
five or six wagons
and about a thousand fools.

308
00:32:39.681 --> 00:32:43.425
- Thank you. Ohh─
- Come on. Meegosh.

309
00:32:47.772 --> 00:32:51.516
It's gonna be all right.
little bobbin.

310
00:32:57.449 --> 00:33:01.363
Everything's gonna be all right.

311
00:33:04.748 --> 00:33:07.741
- Excuse me. sir.
- Out of the way. peck!

312
00:33:09.794 --> 00:33:12.127
Uh. pardon me.

313
00:33:12.214 --> 00:33:14.297
Uh─

314
00:33:19.971 --> 00:33:25.183
Excuse me. sir. We found one
of your babies in our village.

315
00:33:25.268 --> 00:33:28.136
Will you please take care of her?

316
00:33:28.230 --> 00:33:32.600
We're going into battle. little ones.
Find a woman to take care of her.

317
00:33:34.110 --> 00:33:37.228
They thought you were a woman. Airk.

318
00:33:37.322 --> 00:33:39.689
Well─

319
00:33:39.783 --> 00:33:42.321
Madmartigan! What did you do this time?

320
00:33:42.410 --> 00:33:44.367
Nothing you wouldn't have done.

321
00:33:44.454 --> 00:33:46.787
I always knew
you'd end up in a crow's cage.

322
00:33:46.873 --> 00:33:48.705
At least I'm not down there
herding sheep.

323
00:33:48.792 --> 00:33:50.283
What are you doing this far north?

324
00:33:50.377 --> 00:33:53.370
The Nockmaar army
destroyed Galladoorn.

325
00:33:53.463 --> 00:33:55.079
The castle?

326
00:33:55.173 --> 00:33:57.210
Bavmorda's troops are
crushing everything in sight.

327
00:33:57.300 --> 00:33:59.212
Come on. Let me out of here. Airk.

328
00:33:59.302 --> 00:34:01.510
Give me a sword.
I'll win this war for you.

329
00:34:01.596 --> 00:34:06.011
Madmartigan. I still serve Galladoorn.

330
00:34:06.101 --> 00:34:08.058
You serve no one.

331
00:34:08.144 --> 00:34:10.386
Remember?

332
00:34:10.480 --> 00:34:13.689
Sit in your coffin and rot.

333
00:34:13.775 --> 00:34:16.813
Wait. Airk. You need me!

334
00:34:16.903 --> 00:34:19.316
I'll be around long after you're dead!

335
00:34:19.406 --> 00:34:22.023
When I get out of here.
I'm gonna cut your head off...

336
00:34:22.117 --> 00:34:24.200
and stick it on a pig pole!

337
00:34:41.720 --> 00:34:46.465
I miss Kiaya and the bobbins.

338
00:34:50.854 --> 00:34:52.891
We're running out of food.

339
00:34:55.692 --> 00:34:57.934
Nobody's gonna take care of that baby.

340
00:34:58.028 --> 00:35:00.896
You know why? Nobody cares.

341
00:35:03.908 --> 00:35:05.991
Except me.

342
00:35:07.120 --> 00:35:11.706
You want to go back to your families.
I want out of this cage.

343
00:35:11.791 --> 00:35:15.751
Let me take care of that baby.
I'll look after her like she was my own.

344
00:35:15.837 --> 00:35:18.796
I believe he would. Willow.

345
00:35:18.882 --> 00:35:21.420
He doesn't know anything about babies.

346
00:35:21.509 --> 00:35:26.721
Right. But I know a lot of women who do.

347
00:35:26.806 --> 00:35:29.719
If I had somebody in my life.

348
00:35:29.809 --> 00:35:33.393
a little daughter. perhaps.

349
00:35:33.480 --> 00:35:36.723
I might have a reason to go on living.

350
00:35:39.986 --> 00:35:42.820
You can't leave me in here to die.

351
00:35:42.906 --> 00:35:45.899
Not when all I want to do is protect her.

352
00:35:59.255 --> 00:36:03.124
I feel better!

353
00:36:03.259 --> 00:36:06.923
- You've done the right thing! Whoo!
- Okay. All right. All right.

354
00:36:07.013 --> 00:36:11.508
- You gotta promise to feed her.
- Come to Daddy. little darlin'.

355
00:36:11.601 --> 00:36:14.765
- And keep her clean.
- Absolutely.

356
00:36:16.648 --> 00:36:19.085
Hee. hee. hee!

357
00:36:19.175 --> 00:36:23.645
Wheee!

358
00:36:24.823 --> 00:36:26.985
She likes me.

359
00:36:29.077 --> 00:36:31.444
Here are her changing rags.

360
00:36:31.538 --> 00:36:33.746
- And her milk bladder.
- Any milk in there?

361
00:36:33.832 --> 00:36:37.997
- It's for her!
- I wouldn't steal from a baby.

362
00:36:40.964 --> 00:36:43.377
You worry too much. peck.

363
00:36:43.466 --> 00:36:46.584
- It's Willow.
- I mean Willow.

364
00:36:47.971 --> 00:36:53.217
Now listen. boys─ Willow.
You've done the right thing.

365
00:36:53.309 --> 00:36:56.598
Now I want you to get home
and bring your crop in.

366
00:37:02.694 --> 00:37:05.061
Good-bye. little one.

367
00:37:16.207 --> 00:37:18.324
Please take good care of her.

368
00:37:20.670 --> 00:37:22.957
I give you my word of honor!

369
00:37:30.263 --> 00:37:33.597
- Meegosh. slow down!
- Oh. come on!

370
00:37:33.683 --> 00:37:37.893
If we hurry. we can be home by
tomorrow morning. We'll be heroes.

371
00:37:37.979 --> 00:37:41.472
- Do you really think so?
- Sure.

372
00:37:41.566 --> 00:37:43.808
"Look. there's Willow and Meegosh.

373
00:37:43.902 --> 00:37:46.144
The heroes have come home."

374
00:37:46.237 --> 00:37:49.275
"Welcome back. boys.
You deserve medals!"

375
00:37:49.365 --> 00:37:53.609
Yeah. Medals.

376
00:37:53.703 --> 00:37:56.946
Meegosh─

377
00:37:59.292 --> 00:38:03.457
- Did we do the right thing?
- Absolutely.

378
00:38:03.546 --> 00:38:07.711
There's nothing to worry about.

379
00:38:10.804 --> 00:38:13.091
Hyah! Ha ha!

380
00:38:13.181 --> 00:38:18.393
I stole a baby! I stole a baby!

381
00:38:18.478 --> 00:38:22.188
- Hyah!
- That's my baby!

382
00:38:22.315 --> 00:38:24.272
Stop! Wait! Come back!

383
00:38:24.359 --> 00:38:27.443
Left. you stupid bird. Left! Ha ha!

384
00:38:31.407 --> 00:38:33.990
Ow!

385
00:38:34.077 --> 00:38:37.366
Brownies! Let's get out of here!

386
00:38:37.455 --> 00:38:40.698
- Come on. Meegosh!
- Ow!

387
00:38:46.798 --> 00:38:48.790
We'll outrun 'em!

388
00:38:53.596 --> 00:38:56.930
Hey. ugly. wake up!

389
00:38:57.767 --> 00:39:00.180
Huh?

390
00:39:00.311 --> 00:39:05.352
Stand your ground. He's our prisoner.

391
00:39:05.441 --> 00:39:08.184
Meegosh. where's the baby?

392
00:39:08.278 --> 00:39:10.190
Bring the Nelwyns to me.

393
00:39:10.280 --> 00:39:11.691
All right. you heard her!

394
00:39:11.781 --> 00:39:15.525
- What's going on?
- Shut up. or I'll break your nose.

395
00:39:15.618 --> 00:39:18.031
You are mine to toy with.

396
00:39:18.121 --> 00:39:21.580
Forward!

397
00:39:21.666 --> 00:39:25.455
Gimme the rope.

398
00:39:25.545 --> 00:39:29.539
Where─ Where...

399
00:39:29.632 --> 00:39:31.874
did you get that baby?

400
00:39:31.968 --> 00:39:36.679
I stole it from a stupid Daikini.

401
00:39:36.890 --> 00:39:40.008
Franjean. release the Nelwyns.

402
00:39:40.143 --> 00:39:44.387
- And stop pestering them.
- Uh-oh.

403
00:39:48.818 --> 00:39:50.810
Yaah!

404
00:39:59.579 --> 00:40:01.662
Welcome to my kingdom.

405
00:40:09.589 --> 00:40:14.084
- I'm happy to meet you. Willow Ufgood.
- How do you know my name?

406
00:40:14.177 --> 00:40:17.420
Elora Danan told me.

407
00:40:17.513 --> 00:40:20.722
Elora? Elora. Willow is here.

408
00:40:23.603 --> 00:40:29.144
- But she's just a baby.
- She's very special.

409
00:40:29.233 --> 00:40:34.570
My Brownies have been searching for her
ever since we heard she was born.

410
00:40:35.698 --> 00:40:39.567
Elora Danan has chosen you
to be her guardian.

411
00:40:39.661 --> 00:40:44.702
- Me?
- Yes. She likes you.

412
00:40:45.875 --> 00:40:50.791
And Elora Danan knows
you have the courage to help us.

413
00:40:50.880 --> 00:40:54.464
Take my wand to the sorceress
Fin Raziel.

414
00:40:54.550 --> 00:40:58.794
She will guide you and Elora Danan
to the kingdom of Tir Asleen...

415
00:40:58.888 --> 00:41:01.972
where a good king and queen
will look after her.

416
00:41:02.058 --> 00:41:05.768
You need a warrior for a job like this.
I'm a nobody.

417
00:41:05.853 --> 00:41:09.221
Elora. you don't want me.

418
00:41:09.315 --> 00:41:13.025
Tell her. I'm short. even for a Nelwyn.

419
00:41:17.240 --> 00:41:19.323
Hello?

420
00:41:25.957 --> 00:41:29.325
Elora Danan must survive!

421
00:41:29.419 --> 00:41:34.335
She must fulfill her destiny and bring
about the downfall of Queen Bavmorda.

422
00:41:34.424 --> 00:41:37.167
whose powers are growing
like an evil plague.

423
00:41:37.260 --> 00:41:41.675
Unless she is stopped.
Bavmorda will control the lives...

424
00:41:41.764 --> 00:41:46.259
of your village. your children─ everyone.

425
00:41:50.940 --> 00:41:54.433
All creatures of good heart
need your help. Willow.

426
00:41:55.778 --> 00:41:58.316
The choice is yours.

427
00:42:22.889 --> 00:42:26.553
- Hey. Meegosh. Wake up.
- Huh?

428
00:42:26.642 --> 00:42:30.852
- It's time to go home.
- Home?

429
00:42:33.441 --> 00:42:38.152
Listen. Meegosh. Tell Kiaya I love her.

430
00:42:38.237 --> 00:42:41.605
- And I think of her every day.
- Willow─

431
00:42:41.699 --> 00:42:45.158
And tell her I'm not going to let
anything happen to the baby.

432
00:42:45.244 --> 00:42:47.861
Are you sure
you know what you're doing?

433
00:42:49.499 --> 00:42:52.242
I hope so.

434
00:42:52.335 --> 00:42:54.497
Listen. be careful.

435
00:43:00.676 --> 00:43:04.911
- I know the way. Franjean.
- You always think you know the way.

436
00:43:04.998 --> 00:43:06.630
I am the leader!

437
00:43:06.658 --> 00:43:08.562
How long will it take
to find this Raziel?

438
00:43:08.587 --> 00:43:09.621
Not long.

439
00:43:09.685 --> 00:43:13.269
She's been exiled to an island
just over those hills.

440
00:43:13.356 --> 00:43:16.440
- She's what?
- Exiled...

441
00:43:16.526 --> 00:43:20.361
by the evil Queen Bavmorda.

442
00:43:20.446 --> 00:43:23.063
Rool. you fool. He does not need
to know everything.

443
00:43:23.199 --> 00:43:25.691
- I didn't tell him everything.
- You told him enough.

444
00:43:25.827 --> 00:43:28.114
- You mentioned the island. the queen.
- Wait a minute.

445
00:43:28.204 --> 00:43:30.821
So?

446
00:43:30.915 --> 00:43:33.703
What do you mean?
What are you saying. mysterious island?

447
00:43:33.793 --> 00:43:36.456
Don't play with that wand.

448
00:43:36.546 --> 00:43:39.038
Cherlindrea told you it holds vast powers.

449
00:43:39.132 --> 00:43:41.624
Only a great sorcerer can use it.

450
00:43:41.717 --> 00:43:44.425
not a stupid peck like you.

451
00:43:44.512 --> 00:43:47.630
- This way.
- No. No. No. I don't think so.

452
00:43:47.723 --> 00:43:50.010
- All right. then this way.
- Eh. nope.

453
00:43:50.101 --> 00:43:52.639
- This way.
- This way?

454
00:43:52.728 --> 00:43:56.438
- That's what I said.
- This way.

455
00:43:56.524 --> 00:43:59.983
- You sure you know where you're going?
- Of course.

456
00:44:00.069 --> 00:44:02.732
With us as your guides.
no harm will befall you.

457
00:44:13.166 --> 00:44:17.285
Take it up!

458
00:44:18.838 --> 00:44:23.082
- We are not going in there!
- But Elora needs fresh milk.

459
00:44:23.176 --> 00:44:28.012
- And we are drenched.
- You are not in command. shorty. I am!

460
00:44:28.097 --> 00:44:31.716
You hear me? Whoa!

461
00:45:09.472 --> 00:45:11.930
Excuse me? Excuse me.

462
00:45:12.016 --> 00:45:14.975
Could you spare some milk
for this poor hungry baby?

463
00:45:15.061 --> 00:45:19.351
- Get out of here. peck!
- Get outta here or we'll cook ya!

464
00:45:34.205 --> 00:45:36.618
Ooh. look at her!

465
00:45:36.707 --> 00:45:38.949
I could use a love potion on her!

466
00:45:39.043 --> 00:45:42.878
Franjean! Hey!
Give me that dust of broken heart.

467
00:45:42.964 --> 00:45:44.671
Come on! Give it to me!

468
00:45:44.757 --> 00:45:48.091
It's very dangerous.
It belongs to the fairies!

469
00:45:52.265 --> 00:45:54.348
Hey. quiet! You want to get us killed?

470
00:46:01.274 --> 00:46:04.984
Oh. Rool! Always playing
with those fairy love potions.

471
00:46:07.321 --> 00:46:12.407
You are so beautiful!

472
00:46:12.535 --> 00:46:16.119
Your eyes! Your whiskers!

473
00:46:16.247 --> 00:46:18.864
- I have to kiss you!
- Rool!

474
00:46:18.958 --> 00:46:20.699
That dust of broken heart!

475
00:46:35.558 --> 00:46:37.766
Beer!

476
00:46:40.896 --> 00:46:43.013
These people are crazy!
This could be bad!

477
00:46:47.570 --> 00:46:49.607
Hurry! Hurry!

478
00:46:49.697 --> 00:46:51.484
My husband's coming!

479
00:46:51.574 --> 00:46:53.657
If he catches you here.
he'll kill us both!

480
00:46:53.743 --> 00:46:56.406
- How do I look?
- Not you!

481
00:46:57.580 --> 00:46:59.492
Where the hell did you come from?

482
00:46:59.582 --> 00:47:01.824
I knew I shouldn't have trusted you.

483
00:47:01.917 --> 00:47:05.627
Don't I know you?
I stole the baby from you. Daikini.

484
00:47:05.755 --> 00:47:07.963
- while you were taking a pee-pee!
- Cover your face!

485
00:47:08.090 --> 00:47:11.709
- You are crawling with Brownies.
- I hate Brownies!

486
00:47:11.802 --> 00:47:14.545
Whoa!

487
00:47:14.638 --> 00:47:17.221
- Where is he? Where?
- Hello. dear.

488
00:47:17.308 --> 00:47:19.675
There's nobody here
but me and. uh. my. uh─

489
00:47:19.769 --> 00:47:22.182
- I'll kill him!
- ...my cousin. Hilda.

490
00:47:22.271 --> 00:47:24.479
- Hilda?
- Hilda.

491
00:47:24.607 --> 00:47:26.690
- Oh. Hilda!
- This is my husband. Llug.

492
00:47:26.776 --> 00:47:29.519
- Mm. Big husband.
- Yes.

493
00:47:29.653 --> 00:47:31.485
How do you do?

494
00:47:31.572 --> 00:47:33.859
Hilda! Ooh.

495
00:47:33.949 --> 00:47:36.111
Come on. girly. Don't be shy.

496
00:47:36.202 --> 00:47:38.785
Hey! Give her back!

497
00:47:38.913 --> 00:47:41.280
- Pecks make terrible nursemaids.
- Nursemaid?

498
00:47:41.374 --> 00:47:44.242
They get too excited.

499
00:47:44.335 --> 00:47:46.952
Excuse me! Are we having a party?

500
00:47:47.046 --> 00:47:49.083
- Huh?
- Hey. hey. hey. hey!

501
00:47:49.173 --> 00:47:53.793
Stop. please. Ooh.

502
00:47:53.886 --> 00:47:55.718
Come on. Fight like a man!

503
00:47:55.805 --> 00:47:58.843
Want to breed?

504
00:47:58.933 --> 00:48:01.926
Tempting. but no.

505
00:48:04.855 --> 00:48:06.721
Thank you. Time to leave.

506
00:48:06.857 --> 00:48:08.769
- Bye. Hilda!
- Take them out.

507
00:48:08.859 --> 00:48:11.943
Hey! Come along!

508
00:48:12.071 --> 00:48:14.688
- Careful. you lout!
- Move along!

509
00:48:14.782 --> 00:48:17.490
Gather up all these babies.

510
00:48:17.576 --> 00:48:19.818
That baby over there.
Let me see its arm.

511
00:48:23.541 --> 00:48:25.703
That's not the one.

512
00:48:29.380 --> 00:48:32.123
You! Are you the mother of that child?

513
00:48:32.258 --> 00:48:34.841
- Yes. Yes. I am.
- Let me see it.

514
00:48:34.927 --> 00:48:36.509
No! Don't let her!

515
00:48:36.595 --> 00:48:38.052
Aah!

516
00:48:38.139 --> 00:48:40.973
I gave you an order. woman!

517
00:48:50.359 --> 00:48:53.773
You─ You're... beautiful.

518
00:48:53.904 --> 00:48:57.238
- And you're very strong.
- Thank you.

519
00:48:59.785 --> 00:49:02.277
You're no woman!

520
00:49:02.371 --> 00:49:04.158
Now. honey. take it easy.

521
00:49:04.248 --> 00:49:07.161
- Gentlemen.
- Not a woman?

522
00:49:07.251 --> 00:49:10.039
Meet Llug.

523
00:49:11.338 --> 00:49:13.375
- After them!
- Out of the way!

524
00:49:19.680 --> 00:49:20.887
To the horses!

525
00:49:31.442 --> 00:49:33.354
Hyah!

526
00:49:33.444 --> 00:49:37.358
Madmartigan! Madmartigan! Wait!

527
00:49:40.826 --> 00:49:43.569
He's not a woman!

528
00:49:45.789 --> 00:49:48.076
Don't let them get away!

529
00:49:49.835 --> 00:49:53.249
Madmartigan. stop!

530
00:50:12.233 --> 00:50:14.771
Madmartigan. I'm warning you─

531
00:50:16.779 --> 00:50:20.443
- Ow!
- Prepare to die!

532
00:50:43.847 --> 00:50:46.180
Madmartigan! Stop!

533
00:51:02.199 --> 00:51:05.363
No... more... beer.

534
00:51:16.255 --> 00:51:18.338
Franjean. help me!

535
00:51:22.928 --> 00:51:24.794
- Rool!
- Help!

536
00:51:24.888 --> 00:51:28.006
Rool! Rool.

537
00:51:29.184 --> 00:51:32.973
- Rool! What are you doing?
- Help me!

538
00:51:38.319 --> 00:51:40.561
- Come on. I am.
- Pull me in.

539
00:51:40.654 --> 00:51:43.146
Yeah. pull!

540
00:52:09.224 --> 00:52:10.931
Whoa!

541
00:52:17.691 --> 00:52:21.230
Rool. this isn't funny!
Help me cut the rope!

542
00:52:34.416 --> 00:52:37.159
Who-oa!

543
00:52:58.649 --> 00:53:01.266
Willow. stay down!

544
00:53:04.988 --> 00:53:07.025
Whoa!

545
00:53:07.116 --> 00:53:09.278
Whoa!

546
00:53:09.368 --> 00:53:11.325
Have you gone crazy?

547
00:53:11.412 --> 00:53:13.629
You can't chase around
with Elora like this.

548
00:53:13.722 --> 00:53:16.035
- We're getting off!
- Hyah!

549
00:53:16.125 --> 00:53:18.742
Hyah!

550
00:53:41.525 --> 00:53:43.983
Whoa! Whoa!

551
00:53:47.239 --> 00:53:49.572
Oh. Rool.

552
00:53:49.658 --> 00:53:52.321
Now we stop. peck.

553
00:53:53.412 --> 00:53:58.703
Stupid Daikini.
Ask him to stop the wagon.

554
00:53:58.792 --> 00:54:03.002
Madmartigan! You never. ever
drive that fast with an infant!

555
00:54:04.423 --> 00:54:07.006
I just saved that infant's life!

556
00:54:08.469 --> 00:54:10.756
Hah! Hah!

557
00:54:10.846 --> 00:54:12.758
Gather your wits. Come on.

558
00:54:12.848 --> 00:54:15.886
- Don't worry about me.
- Come on!

559
00:54:16.935 --> 00:54:19.143
Get down!

560
00:54:19.229 --> 00:54:21.642
Uh. where am I? Oh!

561
00:54:23.525 --> 00:54:25.608
Rool. you fool. get out of the road!

562
00:54:42.085 --> 00:54:44.668
- Ah. Franjean!
- You better clear out. Willow.

563
00:54:44.755 --> 00:54:46.212
Before those troops come back.

564
00:54:46.298 --> 00:54:49.757
- Ah. my head!
- We don't need him. Elora.

565
00:54:58.143 --> 00:55:00.226
Madmartigan. wait!

566
00:55:00.312 --> 00:55:03.646
Go home. Willow!
It's a dangerous world.

567
00:55:03.732 --> 00:55:05.689
Yeah. and that's why we need your help.

568
00:55:05.776 --> 00:55:08.985
My help?
What do you need my help for?

569
00:55:09.071 --> 00:55:11.188
You're a sorcerer!

570
00:55:11.281 --> 00:55:14.524
You're a great warrior
and a swordsman.

571
00:55:14.618 --> 00:55:17.486
And you're ten times
bigger than I am. stupid!

572
00:55:17.579 --> 00:55:20.822
Are you trying to make my life
more difficult than it already is?

573
00:55:24.127 --> 00:55:28.997
Hurry! Big dogs!

574
00:55:29.091 --> 00:55:33.335
Look. I'm sorry I got angry.

575
00:55:33.428 --> 00:55:35.385
We wouldn't have escaped without you.

576
00:55:49.528 --> 00:55:52.396
Well. don't expect me to help you again.

577
00:55:53.866 --> 00:55:57.485
Good! Then we go that way!
To the lake!

578
00:55:58.579 --> 00:56:01.697
That way.

579
00:56:01.790 --> 00:56:05.374
You are drunk. and when
you are drunk. you forget that...

580
00:56:05.460 --> 00:56:07.372
- I am in charge!
- You are in charge.

581
00:56:07.462 --> 00:56:09.670
Fine.
Then which way do we go?

582
00:56:09.756 --> 00:56:11.748
That way!

583
00:56:14.803 --> 00:56:19.343
Oh. no! That's the way I'm going.

584
00:56:19.433 --> 00:56:22.392
All right. all right.
You can follow me as far as the lake.

585
00:56:22.477 --> 00:56:24.639
But that's it!

586
00:56:24.730 --> 00:56:28.519
- You're not going south. are you?
- No. just as far as the lake.

587
00:56:28.609 --> 00:56:33.729
Good. Mumbo. Jumbo. I am hungry.
Go get me some eggs or something.

588
00:56:33.822 --> 00:56:36.439
- We are not afraid of you!
- Now!

589
00:56:43.165 --> 00:56:47.830
Kael. have you found the child?

590
00:56:47.920 --> 00:56:49.661
The search goes on. my queen.

591
00:56:50.714 --> 00:56:52.751
Why. with my powers.

592
00:56:52.841 --> 00:56:56.050
with the strength of my great army.

593
00:56:56.136 --> 00:56:59.504
can you not find one little child?

594
00:56:59.598 --> 00:57:01.931
We look even now. It won't be long.

595
00:57:02.017 --> 00:57:05.385
Find the child. Find the child!

596
00:57:05.479 --> 00:57:08.062
Time is running out.

597
00:57:15.572 --> 00:57:18.406
- Good night.
- She is kinda cute.

598
00:57:20.118 --> 00:57:21.859
When she's quiet.

599
00:57:23.246 --> 00:57:25.203
She's really a princess.

600
00:57:25.290 --> 00:57:29.284
Really? And you're a great sorcerer.

601
00:57:29.378 --> 00:57:31.290
And I'm the king of Kashmir.

602
00:57:31.380 --> 00:57:35.169
Go to sleep. Willow.

603
00:57:35.258 --> 00:57:37.750
Good night. Madmartigan.

604
00:57:37.844 --> 00:57:40.803
Rats! Big rats! Rats!

605
00:57:40.889 --> 00:57:44.178
Uh─ Uh! Oh! Rats! Ra─

606
00:57:44.267 --> 00:57:49.183
Oh. Rool. you and that
stupid rat dream! Ha!

607
00:57:57.948 --> 00:58:00.691
Tuatha...

608
00:58:00.784 --> 00:58:02.901
Lawkathok...

609
00:58:02.995 --> 00:58:04.952
Tuatha!

610
00:58:05.038 --> 00:58:07.746
Huh? Willow?

611
00:58:08.792 --> 00:58:10.954
Willow?

612
00:58:12.754 --> 00:58:15.167
Oh.
There you are.

613
00:58:15.257 --> 00:58:17.214
Madmartigan!

614
00:58:17.300 --> 00:58:20.634
Night. Willow.

615
00:58:32.691 --> 00:58:34.774
This way! This way!

616
00:58:46.496 --> 00:58:48.408
What are you doing?

617
00:58:48.498 --> 00:58:50.865
I found some black root.
She loves it!

618
00:58:50.959 --> 00:58:53.872
Black root?
I am the father of two children.

619
00:58:53.962 --> 00:58:55.999
and you never. ever
give a baby black root.

620
00:58:56.089 --> 00:58:59.207
Well. my mother raised us on black root.

621
00:58:59.301 --> 00:59:01.839
It's good for ya!
It puts hair on your chest.

622
00:59:01.970 --> 00:59:04.633
- Doesn't it. Sticks?
- Her name is not Sticks.

623
00:59:04.723 --> 00:59:07.636
She's Elora Danan.
the future empress of Tir Asleen.

624
00:59:07.726 --> 00:59:10.059
And the last thing she's gonna want
is a hairy chest!

625
00:59:14.232 --> 00:59:16.224
Did you see what he did?

626
00:59:16.318 --> 00:59:19.607
He stole our black root.
I'll get some more. Don't worry about it.

627
00:59:24.493 --> 00:59:27.827
There it is! The island!

628
00:59:29.998 --> 00:59:31.955
We made it.

629
00:59:32.042 --> 00:59:36.537
We have led you to the
island of the sorceress Fin Raziel.

630
00:59:36.671 --> 00:59:40.961
- We'll get a boat in that village.
- A big boat..

631
00:59:58.944 --> 01:00:00.981
Well. looks like I got you here.

632
01:00:01.071 --> 01:00:03.438
You! What did you do?

633
01:00:03.532 --> 01:00:06.616
All you did was hang around
and eat our eggs! Huh?

634
01:00:06.701 --> 01:00:08.658
I found a boat. We're all set.

635
01:00:08.745 --> 01:00:12.614
Good. Take these two lizards
out and drown them.

636
01:00:12.749 --> 01:00:15.992
- Lizards! Who are you calling lizards?
- Heh? Heh?

637
01:00:18.171 --> 01:00:20.788
Your mother was a lizard!

638
01:00:23.844 --> 01:00:26.382
Good-bye. Sticks.

639
01:00:28.974 --> 01:00:33.309
If you really are a princess.
take care of him.

640
01:00:41.319 --> 01:00:44.608
- Madmartigan!
- What?

641
01:00:44.698 --> 01:00:46.564
Thanks.

642
01:00:56.084 --> 01:00:58.622
Hey! Aah!

643
01:00:58.712 --> 01:01:02.001
- Keep walkin'. hero!
- Don't even turn around!

644
01:01:03.258 --> 01:01:06.217
It's all right. Elora.

645
01:01:06.303 --> 01:01:08.716
Go to sleep.

646
01:01:08.805 --> 01:01:12.799
Nobody'll find you here.
I'll be back with Fin Raziel very soon.

647
01:01:12.893 --> 01:01:16.227
We will guard her with our meager lives.

648
01:01:44.507 --> 01:01:47.295
Raziel!

649
01:01:47.385 --> 01:01:51.220
Fin Raziel! I have to talk to you. please!

650
01:01:55.143 --> 01:01:57.726
Raziel!

651
01:02:02.567 --> 01:02:06.231
She's not here.

652
01:02:09.199 --> 01:02:11.156
Aah!

653
01:02:11.243 --> 01:02:14.782
Get back! Who are you?

654
01:02:15.914 --> 01:02:18.827
Who are you?

655
01:02:21.211 --> 01:02:24.295
- I'm Willow Ufgood.
- What are you doing here?

656
01:02:24.381 --> 01:02:28.045
I've come to find
the great sorceress. Fin Raziel.

657
01:02:28.134 --> 01:02:30.717
That's me! I'm Raziel!

658
01:02:32.722 --> 01:02:34.679
This can't be right!

659
01:02:34.766 --> 01:02:38.305
One of Bavmorda's spells
transformed me.

660
01:02:40.563 --> 01:02:43.146
Believe me. it could have been worse!

661
01:02:43.233 --> 01:02:49.025
Oh. Well. this wand is for you.
It's from Cherlindrea.

662
01:02:49.114 --> 01:02:53.609
Then the prophecy is true.
The princess has been born.

663
01:02:53.702 --> 01:02:55.659
Take me to her.

664
01:02:58.206 --> 01:03:00.949
It is Elora Danan.

665
01:03:01.042 --> 01:03:03.955
Isn't she beautiful?

666
01:03:04.045 --> 01:03:07.004
Isn't she beautiful?

667
01:03:07.090 --> 01:03:10.549
- That's Raziel?
- I don't know. I─

668
01:03:10.635 --> 01:03:12.877
I expected something more grand.
Less. uh─

669
01:03:12.971 --> 01:03:14.928
- Fuzzy.
- Fuzzy!

670
01:03:15.015 --> 01:03:18.804
You must use the wand.
Turn me back into my human form.

671
01:03:18.893 --> 01:03:22.227
- What do I do?
- You mean you're not a sorcerer?

672
01:03:23.481 --> 01:03:25.939
Yes. Sorta.

673
01:03:26.067 --> 01:03:28.605
I'm a farmer.

674
01:03:28.695 --> 01:03:30.561
But I do know a few tricks.

675
01:03:30.655 --> 01:03:35.901
Tricks? Cherlindrea sent you?
You must learn real magic.

676
01:03:37.926 --> 01:03:40.183
- Horses!
- Horses!

677
01:03:40.248 --> 01:03:42.740
Quick! Take her!
Hurry! Hurry!

678
01:03:51.593 --> 01:03:54.586
I knew he was a traitor!

679
01:03:57.140 --> 01:03:59.757
- Sorry about this. peck.
- Keep your mouth shut!

680
01:04:00.935 --> 01:04:03.678
Told you we'd find him without your help.

681
01:04:03.772 --> 01:04:05.729
- Give me that baby.
- No!

682
01:04:09.194 --> 01:04:13.154
- Give her back!
- Leave me alone! Don't touch me!

683
01:04:19.079 --> 01:04:20.945
This is the one we're looking for.

684
01:04:21.039 --> 01:04:24.453
We must take it back to Nockmaar.

685
01:04:27.212 --> 01:04:29.124
Lose your skirt?

686
01:04:36.805 --> 01:04:38.717
I've still got what counts.

687
01:04:38.807 --> 01:04:41.140
Not for long.

688
01:04:46.981 --> 01:04:50.520
- Bring him.
- Over here!

689
01:05:08.211 --> 01:05:10.874
We'll never keep up with those horses.

690
01:05:11.005 --> 01:05:14.419
- Then we will have to track them.
- That would take forever.

691
01:05:14.509 --> 01:05:17.252
Besides. even if we find them.
they'll catch us.

692
01:05:17.345 --> 01:05:20.509
stick us in cages. torture us
and finally devour us.

693
01:05:20.598 --> 01:05:22.510
Are you suggesting we go home?

694
01:05:22.642 --> 01:05:25.510
- Nah. This is more fun!
- All right.

695
01:05:25.603 --> 01:05:27.560
Fine. then. Come on!

696
01:05:41.369 --> 01:05:44.783
I'm worried about Elora.
She doesn't sound good.

697
01:05:44.873 --> 01:05:47.616
Hurry! Practice the chant I taught you!

698
01:05:47.709 --> 01:05:53.501
Tanna... looatha─
Oh. I can't remember the middle part.

699
01:05:53.590 --> 01:05:55.627
Locktwaar!

700
01:05:55.717 --> 01:05:58.710
That's the word that pleads for change.

701
01:05:58.803 --> 01:06:00.669
Locktwaar.

702
01:06:04.392 --> 01:06:07.510
Elora's cold and hungry. She knows me.

703
01:06:07.604 --> 01:06:09.561
Please. let me take care of her.

704
01:06:09.647 --> 01:06:11.764
I don't need help from a peck.

705
01:06:15.528 --> 01:06:19.522
- What are you staring at?
- Your leg.

706
01:06:19.616 --> 01:06:21.983
I'd like to break it.

707
01:06:22.076 --> 01:06:24.693
You may find that difficult. slave.

708
01:06:24.787 --> 01:06:26.949
while I'm up here and you're down there.

709
01:06:30.084 --> 01:06:32.292
I hate that woman.

710
01:07:04.953 --> 01:07:06.990
Hyah!

711
01:07:10.833 --> 01:07:13.621
I found it. Kael.

712
01:07:14.754 --> 01:07:17.792
That should make my mother happy.

713
01:07:17.882 --> 01:07:20.875
What are they gonna do to her?

714
01:07:33.439 --> 01:07:36.102
Hither walha...

715
01:07:36.192 --> 01:07:39.685
bairn deru bordak...

716
01:07:39.821 --> 01:07:41.733
bellanockt.

717
01:07:41.823 --> 01:07:44.611
That's magic?
Smells terrible.

718
01:07:44.742 --> 01:07:47.951
- It's the life spark. It forms after─
- Well. it stinks!

719
01:07:48.037 --> 01:07:51.246
- This whole thing stinks!
- Ignore him. Willow.

720
01:07:51.332 --> 01:07:54.245
- He's a fool!
- If only I had a sword!

721
01:07:54.377 --> 01:07:57.495
If only you'd quit talking about it.

722
01:07:57.589 --> 01:08:00.923
Willow. you must transform me
to my human self.

723
01:08:01.009 --> 01:08:03.843
But. Raziel. I'm not ready yet.

724
01:08:03.928 --> 01:08:07.137
You'd better be. Get me down.

725
01:08:10.768 --> 01:08:13.181
Ow!

726
01:08:15.773 --> 01:08:18.911
Why don't you help me get out of here
instead of chattering with that muskrat?

727
01:08:19.001 --> 01:08:21.609
Muskrat! When I change back...

728
01:08:21.696 --> 01:08:25.656
to my former self.
I will crush this army...

729
01:08:25.742 --> 01:08:28.405
and take Elora Danan to Tir Asleen...

730
01:08:28.494 --> 01:08:31.077
where she will be safe.

731
01:08:31.164 --> 01:08:33.451
Ow!

732
01:08:33.541 --> 01:08:35.498
What'd you bite me for?

733
01:08:35.585 --> 01:08:38.874
You need three drops
of your blood to put in the potion.

734
01:08:38.963 --> 01:08:42.252
Well. you could've warned me.

735
01:08:42.342 --> 01:08:44.755
For beginners. there's some pain.

736
01:08:44.844 --> 01:08:49.930
but don't let anything
break your concentration.

737
01:08:55.063 --> 01:08:57.897
Hither greenan bairn claideb lunanockt.

738
01:08:58.024 --> 01:09:01.768
- Hello. everybody! We have arrived!
- You are saved.

739
01:09:01.861 --> 01:09:04.695
- Shh!
- Don't interrupt.

740
01:09:06.115 --> 01:09:09.279
Hither greenan bairn claideb lunanockt.

741
01:09:09.369 --> 01:09:12.203
What are you gonna look like
if this works?

742
01:09:12.288 --> 01:09:14.746
- Don't interrupt.
- Sorry.

743
01:09:14.832 --> 01:09:16.789
Hither greenan bairn claideb lunanockt.

744
01:09:16.876 --> 01:09:20.165
I am a young. beautiful woman.

745
01:09:20.254 --> 01:09:22.041
Concentrate. Willow.

746
01:09:22.131 --> 01:09:24.293
Hither greenan bairn claideb lunanockt.

747
01:09:24.384 --> 01:09:26.751
Hither greenan bairn claideb lunanockt.

748
01:09:26.844 --> 01:09:28.927
No! You're losing me!

749
01:09:29.055 --> 01:09:32.469
Hither greenan bairn claideb lunanockt.

750
01:09:35.436 --> 01:09:37.302
Hither greenan bairn claideb─

751
01:09:37.438 --> 01:09:40.431
- Aah! Aah!
- You all right? Nice try. Willow.

752
01:09:48.533 --> 01:09:52.493
Farmers! Cherlindrea sends me farmers!

753
01:09:52.578 --> 01:09:56.037
Whew!
The Nelwyn really butchered that one.

754
01:09:56.124 --> 01:09:57.956
I'm sorry. Raziel.

755
01:09:58.167 --> 01:10:02.377
- You want out?
- Easy. We can pick a lock. Come on.

756
01:10:02.463 --> 01:10:04.375
No. No. no. Like this!

757
01:10:04.465 --> 01:10:06.577
I know what I'm doing.
It's my spear. Leave it alone.

758
01:10:06.667 --> 01:10:10.381
Let me do it. Out of the way. rodents.

759
01:10:11.472 --> 01:10:13.259
Take your hand off that.

760
01:10:13.349 --> 01:10:17.764
You leave that alone.
you stupid. fat Daikini!

761
01:10:17.854 --> 01:10:19.516
Ow!

762
01:10:19.605 --> 01:10:21.688
Dust of broken hearts.

763
01:10:32.452 --> 01:10:35.240
Ha. ha! You are free!

764
01:10:35.329 --> 01:10:39.539
Come on. Madmartigan.
Let's get Elora Danan out of here.

765
01:10:39.667 --> 01:10:43.832
- Yeah. It'll be fun.
- Come on!

766
01:10:55.516 --> 01:10:59.510
- Are you all right?
- Yeah.

767
01:10:59.604 --> 01:11:01.687
I feel... good.

768
01:11:01.814 --> 01:11:05.353
- The dust of broken hearts.
- Ah─

769
01:11:05.443 --> 01:11:07.981
Hey. come on!

770
01:11:13.451 --> 01:11:16.535
- Let me see!
- Let me see. You always see.

771
01:11:16.621 --> 01:11:19.079
There's Elora. right there. on those furs.

772
01:11:21.501 --> 01:11:23.618
Hey. wait! Leave this to us.

773
01:11:23.711 --> 01:11:26.454
- It's too dangerous for you.
- Only one of us should go in there.

774
01:11:26.547 --> 01:11:29.381
I've had experience in this sort of thing.
I know what I'm doing.

775
01:11:56.661 --> 01:11:59.529
Uh-oh.

776
01:11:59.622 --> 01:12:03.582
Wait. Shh. No! No!

777
01:12:14.095 --> 01:12:16.883
- I love you.
- Madmartigan!

778
01:12:17.014 --> 01:12:19.973
- What are you doing?
- Take the baby and go! Come on!

779
01:12:20.059 --> 01:12:21.971
Come on!

780
01:12:32.029 --> 01:12:34.237
- Oh. Sorsha.
- Oh!

781
01:12:35.992 --> 01:12:38.985
Wake from this hateful sleep.

782
01:12:39.078 --> 01:12:41.445
It deprives me of your beauty.

783
01:12:41.539 --> 01:12:45.499
- The beauty of your eyes─
- One move. jackass.

784
01:12:45.585 --> 01:12:47.952
and you really will be a woman.

785
01:12:49.338 --> 01:12:53.252
You are my sun! My moon!

786
01:12:53.342 --> 01:12:57.757
My starlit sky.
Without you. I dwell in darkness.

787
01:12:57.889 --> 01:13:01.974
- I love you.
- What are you doing here?

788
01:13:02.059 --> 01:13:05.393
Your power has enchanted me.
I stand helpless against it.

789
01:13:05.479 --> 01:13:07.391
Come to me. now.

790
01:13:07.481 --> 01:13:09.894
Tonight. let me worship you
in my arms.

791
01:13:10.026 --> 01:13:12.734
- Get away from me!
- I love you!

792
01:13:12.820 --> 01:13:15.278
Stop saying that!

793
01:13:15.364 --> 01:13:19.574
How can I stop the beating of my heart?
It pounds like never before.

794
01:13:19.702 --> 01:13:22.285
- Out of fear.
- Out of love!

795
01:13:22.371 --> 01:13:24.863
I can stop it. I'll kill you.

796
01:13:24.957 --> 01:13:27.870
Death. next to love. is a trivial thing.

797
01:13:30.671 --> 01:13:33.163
Your touch is worth 100.000 deaths.

798
01:13:38.054 --> 01:13:40.717
What goes on here?

799
01:13:44.727 --> 01:13:46.719
Deceiver!

800
01:13:48.314 --> 01:13:50.180
Stop him!

801
01:13:59.116 --> 01:14:01.733
Captain. get up!

802
01:14:12.171 --> 01:14:16.791
You are great.

803
01:14:16.884 --> 01:14:19.752
Get on that shield!

804
01:14:31.107 --> 01:14:33.724
Sorsha!

805
01:14:36.404 --> 01:14:38.396
After them!

806
01:14:45.121 --> 01:14:47.488
Whoa! Hey!

807
01:14:52.294 --> 01:14:54.251
They're getting away!

808
01:15:03.097 --> 01:15:05.305
- Follow me. Rool. I don't know.
- Where are you?

809
01:15:05.433 --> 01:15:09.598
- Aah! Ooh.
- Oh. no. where did everybody go?

810
01:15:09.687 --> 01:15:11.644
Maybe it was something we said.

811
01:16:05.701 --> 01:16:08.819
Ohh-h-h-h!

812
01:16:30.017 --> 01:16:32.009
Madmartigan!

813
01:16:48.828 --> 01:16:53.038
- Madmartigan!
- What the hell happened up there?

814
01:16:53.124 --> 01:16:55.537
You started spouting poetry.

815
01:16:55.626 --> 01:16:58.209
- Poetry?
- Yeah.

816
01:16:58.295 --> 01:17:01.504
"I love you. Sorsha.
I worship you. Sorsha."

817
01:17:01.590 --> 01:17:03.547
You almost got us killed!

818
01:17:03.634 --> 01:17:05.500
"I love you. Sorsha"?

819
01:17:05.594 --> 01:17:08.007
I don't love her.
She kicked me in the face.

820
01:17:08.097 --> 01:17:11.511
I hate her! Don't I?

821
01:17:13.727 --> 01:17:16.140
Kael! Kael!

822
01:17:16.230 --> 01:17:18.893
Nockmaar soldiers!

823
01:17:20.901 --> 01:17:24.360
Hide! Get the children! Come on!

824
01:17:27.116 --> 01:17:29.028
- Get the children!
- They're after us!

825
01:17:29.118 --> 01:17:32.236
Come on. Follow me.
Quick! Come on! Move!

826
01:17:48.721 --> 01:17:51.464
I knew you'd get out of that rattrap.

827
01:17:54.101 --> 01:17:56.013
You left me to die. Airk.

828
01:17:56.103 --> 01:17:59.346
I probably saved your life.
We were slaughtered. and I lost a lot─

829
01:17:59.440 --> 01:18:01.773
Shh! Quiet!

830
01:18:02.860 --> 01:18:04.817
Tear this village apart!

831
01:18:04.904 --> 01:18:09.274
Look everywhere!
Find the child!

832
01:18:18.167 --> 01:18:21.626
Shh!

833
01:18:27.468 --> 01:18:29.380
Shh-shh-shh!

834
01:18:45.110 --> 01:18:48.103
Tell Sorsha I search the north bank!

835
01:18:48.197 --> 01:18:50.109
- Hah! Hah!
- Yes. General.

836
01:19:03.254 --> 01:19:05.337
Quiet. Shh!

837
01:19:24.692 --> 01:19:27.685
- Sorsha!
- Back.

838
01:19:27.778 --> 01:19:29.485
Back!

839
01:19:36.161 --> 01:19:38.653
Back!

840
01:19:38.789 --> 01:19:43.033
- Keep the baby quiet.
- She needs to be changed.

841
01:19:43.127 --> 01:19:44.868
- Nockmaar scum!
- You'll never defeat us.

842
01:19:44.962 --> 01:19:46.749
- Give up the baby!
- Shut up!

843
01:19:48.799 --> 01:19:50.661
What does Bavmorda want
with this baby. anyway?

844
01:19:50.751 --> 01:19:52.258
She's a princess.

845
01:19:52.386 --> 01:19:54.918
- We're taking her to Tir Asleen.
- Tir Asleen?

846
01:19:55.005 --> 01:19:57.173
Even if you could find it. peck.

847
01:19:57.266 --> 01:19:59.633
she's right─ you'd never
get past the Nockmaar army.

848
01:19:59.727 --> 01:20:02.185
There's an even bigger army
at Tir Asleen.

849
01:20:02.271 --> 01:20:04.763
If we can just get there─

850
01:20:08.193 --> 01:20:10.936
I've lost more than half my men
fighting Bavmorda.

851
01:20:11.030 --> 01:20:13.568
Now you and this peck
are gonna take her on?

852
01:20:13.657 --> 01:20:16.900
You always told me you served
no one. Madmartigan.

853
01:20:16.994 --> 01:20:18.951
Since when are you a crusader?

854
01:20:21.248 --> 01:20:24.491
He's not gonna help you. peck.

855
01:20:24.585 --> 01:20:26.577
He's a worthless thief.

856
01:20:27.963 --> 01:20:30.421
I'm not a thief. Airk.

857
01:20:30.507 --> 01:20:33.466
He's not a thief.

858
01:20:33.552 --> 01:20:35.760
Are you?

859
01:20:50.319 --> 01:20:54.154
I serve the Nelwyn. Airk.

860
01:20:58.827 --> 01:21:01.444
- Want to come with us?
- You'll never make it. Madmartigan.

861
01:21:03.415 --> 01:21:05.327
Then once again we say good-bye.

862
01:21:19.139 --> 01:21:22.553
- Over here!
- Sorsha!

863
01:21:22.643 --> 01:21:26.011
Weapons down or she's dead!

864
01:21:31.235 --> 01:21:32.942
Hyah! Hyah!

865
01:21:38.575 --> 01:21:41.488
- Hyah!
- Get to your horses! After 'em!

866
01:22:27.708 --> 01:22:30.166
This way! This way!

867
01:22:30.252 --> 01:22:32.960
As the crow flies. you fools!

868
01:22:39.887 --> 01:22:42.675
- You're holding me too tight!
- I don't want you to get away.

869
01:22:42.764 --> 01:22:47.600
Why? Because I'm your sun.
your moon. your starlit sky?

870
01:22:49.229 --> 01:22:51.437
Get your hair out of my face.
or I'll chop it off.

871
01:22:55.277 --> 01:22:59.191
Did I really─ Did I really
say those things last night?

872
01:22:59.281 --> 01:23:02.399
- In your tent?
- You said you loved me.

873
01:23:02.493 --> 01:23:04.985
- I don't remember that.
- You lied to me!

874
01:23:05.078 --> 01:23:07.491
No. I─

875
01:23:07.581 --> 01:23:09.994
I just wasn't myself last night.

876
01:23:10.083 --> 01:23:14.373
I suppose my power enchanted you.
and you were helpless against it.

877
01:23:14.463 --> 01:23:17.422
- Um. sort of.
- Then what?

878
01:23:17.508 --> 01:23:19.625
It went away.

879
01:23:19.718 --> 01:23:23.337
It went away?
"I dwell in darkness without you."

880
01:23:23.430 --> 01:23:25.513
- and it went away?
- Yeah.

881
01:23:36.652 --> 01:23:40.771
Whoa.

882
01:23:47.579 --> 01:23:49.992
Hurry! Kael's coming!

883
01:23:54.545 --> 01:23:56.832
Madmartigan. come on! Now!

884
01:24:04.846 --> 01:24:08.430
Madmartigan. come on!

885
01:24:08.517 --> 01:24:11.305
They're coming! Away!

886
01:24:11.395 --> 01:24:13.637
Go on! Hyah!

887
01:24:30.664 --> 01:24:33.782
Whoa! Whoa!

888
01:24:33.875 --> 01:24:36.037
This way!

889
01:24:41.550 --> 01:24:45.385
Tir Asleen! At last. Tir Asleen!

890
01:24:56.273 --> 01:24:58.185
Hello?

891
01:24:58.275 --> 01:25:00.813
Hello?

892
01:25:04.948 --> 01:25:08.487
Hello?

893
01:25:08.577 --> 01:25:10.819
Why did I listen to you. peck?

894
01:25:10.912 --> 01:25:14.826
"Everything will be all right
once we get to Tir Asleen."

895
01:25:14.916 --> 01:25:16.999
The only army around here...

896
01:25:17.085 --> 01:25:20.544
is the one that's about to ride
across this valley and wipe us out!

897
01:25:20.631 --> 01:25:23.669
But Cherlindrea said we'd be safe here.

898
01:25:23.759 --> 01:25:27.127
Safe? Look at these people.

899
01:25:27.220 --> 01:25:31.464
This place is cursed. peck.
It's falling apart. Open your eyes!

900
01:25:31.600 --> 01:25:35.219
And it─

901
01:25:35.312 --> 01:25:37.395
Trolls.

902
01:25:39.983 --> 01:25:42.100
I hate trolls.

903
01:25:43.195 --> 01:25:45.608
This is the work of Bavmorda.

904
01:25:54.289 --> 01:25:57.327
Willow? The wand.

905
01:25:57.459 --> 01:26:00.873
- Turn me back into my human form.
- Are you sure?

906
01:26:16.770 --> 01:26:19.012
Yeah.

907
01:26:19.106 --> 01:26:21.143
Good.

908
01:26:27.781 --> 01:26:29.864
Hurry. Willow. Transform me.

909
01:26:29.950 --> 01:26:32.909
I can't do it. I'm just not a sorcerer.

910
01:26:32.994 --> 01:26:35.702
But you can be. Speak...

911
01:26:35.789 --> 01:26:38.452
and be one with the words.

912
01:26:38.542 --> 01:26:42.126
Avalorium. greenan...

913
01:26:42.212 --> 01:26:45.546
luatha. tye─

914
01:26:45.632 --> 01:26:49.592
Oh. Willow. you're losing me.

915
01:26:51.805 --> 01:26:54.923
Madmartigan. Kael's coming!

916
01:26:55.016 --> 01:26:58.009
Willow. you idiot.

917
01:26:58.145 --> 01:27:00.182
- Raziel?
- Willow.

918
01:27:00.272 --> 01:27:02.810
arm that catapult up there.

919
01:27:22.002 --> 01:27:24.335
Whoa! Whoa!

920
01:27:24.421 --> 01:27:29.962
- Good work. Madmartigan.
- What the hell happened to you?

921
01:27:30.051 --> 01:27:32.668
Assault! Sorsha. battering ram!

922
01:27:37.350 --> 01:27:39.342
Cut it down!

923
01:27:50.363 --> 01:27:52.400
Faster!

924
01:28:06.880 --> 01:28:11.215
Forward! Break it down!

925
01:28:30.821 --> 01:28:33.404
Again! Again!

926
01:28:37.994 --> 01:28:40.452
Willow. use the wand on that troll.

927
01:28:42.707 --> 01:28:46.075
Bellalockt!

928
01:28:55.804 --> 01:28:59.718
Ewww!

929
01:29:07.274 --> 01:29:10.767
Break it down! Forward!

930
01:29:26.626 --> 01:29:30.165
Whoa! Whoa!

931
01:29:57.949 --> 01:30:00.362
Get him!

932
01:30:22.182 --> 01:30:23.844
The other side!

933
01:30:38.490 --> 01:30:40.777
Destroy the beast! Find the baby!

934
01:30:40.867 --> 01:30:43.530
Baaa! Take tha-a-a-at!

935
01:31:55.817 --> 01:31:58.104
Willow!

936
01:32:19.674 --> 01:32:22.462
Madmartigan. help!

937
01:32:24.137 --> 01:32:26.675
Willow!

938
01:32:33.730 --> 01:32:37.565
Get him. Madmartigan!

939
01:32:45.784 --> 01:32:47.320
Here.

940
01:33:02.967 --> 01:33:05.175
The baby!

941
01:34:07.073 --> 01:34:10.191
Airk's army. Get Kael!

942
01:34:10.285 --> 01:34:12.698
Airk's army!

943
01:34:15.123 --> 01:34:17.331
- We are here!
- You are rescued!

944
01:34:17.417 --> 01:34:20.376
- Charge!
- Charge!

945
01:34:37.270 --> 01:34:39.683
No mercy!

946
01:34:52.118 --> 01:34:54.952
Elora!

947
01:34:55.038 --> 01:34:57.451
Willow!

948
01:35:03.296 --> 01:35:06.880
- Elora's gone.
- Willow.

949
01:35:06.966 --> 01:35:10.209
They've taken her.
There were too many of them.

950
01:35:10.345 --> 01:35:12.712
Willow.

951
01:35:15.141 --> 01:35:17.428
Can you ride?

952
01:35:20.021 --> 01:35:22.013
Let's ride.

953
01:35:34.452 --> 01:35:36.819
I have the child!

954
01:36:01.271 --> 01:36:03.388
We need towers and a battering ram!

955
01:36:03.481 --> 01:36:06.599
Break out the tents! Make camp!

956
01:36:06.693 --> 01:36:08.776
Make camp!

957
01:36:08.861 --> 01:36:10.693
We'll assault at first light.

958
01:36:24.544 --> 01:36:26.536
Where's Sorsha?

959
01:36:26.629 --> 01:36:29.246
She has turned against us.
Your Highness.

960
01:36:33.553 --> 01:36:37.012
Turned against me?

961
01:36:40.643 --> 01:36:42.760
Prepare for the ritual!

962
01:37:06.336 --> 01:37:09.795
This is not an army.

963
01:37:09.881 --> 01:37:11.793
Willow.

964
01:37:11.883 --> 01:37:14.546
quick. hide.

965
01:37:19.349 --> 01:37:22.433
Use the shelter chant. Protect yourself.

966
01:37:22.518 --> 01:37:24.555
- Why?
- Just do it.

967
01:37:30.109 --> 01:37:34.604
- We've come for Elora Danan.
- You dare to challenge me?

968
01:37:34.697 --> 01:37:36.984
You're not warriors.

969
01:37:37.075 --> 01:37:39.943
You're pigs!

970
01:37:40.078 --> 01:37:44.322
Toa thonna mondarr!

971
01:37:44.415 --> 01:37:48.204
Nocklith! Vohkbar!

972
01:37:55.843 --> 01:37:59.553
You're all pigs!

973
01:37:59.639 --> 01:38:03.223
Pigs!

974
01:38:07.355 --> 01:38:10.314
Avaggdu luatha bairn off haefermore.

975
01:38:18.282 --> 01:38:22.322
Sorsha!

976
01:38:22.412 --> 01:38:25.155
Mother. no!

977
01:38:26.332 --> 01:38:28.289
Kothon!

978
01:38:49.814 --> 01:38:53.433
Avaggdu luatha bairn off haefermore.

979
01:38:53.526 --> 01:38:57.440
Avaggdu luatha bairn off haefermore.

980
01:39:07.707 --> 01:39:09.744
Begin the ritual.

981
01:39:09.834 --> 01:39:12.668
This baby will not destroy me.

982
01:39:16.924 --> 01:39:20.042
Come. thunder!

983
01:39:20.136 --> 01:39:22.924
Come. lightning!

984
01:39:23.014 --> 01:39:27.429
Touch this altar with your powers.

985
01:39:48.372 --> 01:39:50.409
Aah!

986
01:39:50.500 --> 01:39:53.834
We've come all this way
and now Elora Danan's gonna die!

987
01:39:53.920 --> 01:39:56.958
No. we can still defeat Bavmorda.

988
01:39:57.048 --> 01:39:59.165
She's too powerful. Raziel.

989
01:39:59.258 --> 01:40:02.422
Transform me and I will destroy her.

990
01:40:07.225 --> 01:40:11.640
Elements of eternity. above and below.

991
01:40:11.729 --> 01:40:16.440
Balance of essence. fire beget snow.

992
01:40:17.944 --> 01:40:21.062
- Locktwaar danalora luatha danu...
- Willow.

993
01:40:21.197 --> 01:40:24.736
- believe in the words.
- tuatha. tuatha. chnox danu.

994
01:40:24.867 --> 01:40:27.234
- Concentrate.
- Locktwaar danalora...

995
01:40:27.370 --> 01:40:31.284
- luatha danu tuatha. tuatha.
- Oh. no!

996
01:40:31.374 --> 01:40:34.208
Locktwaar danalora.

997
01:40:34.293 --> 01:40:37.377
Locktwaar danalora luatha danu...

998
01:40:37.505 --> 01:40:40.919
- tuatha. tuatha. chnox danu.
- Don't give up.

999
01:40:41.008 --> 01:40:43.671
Willow!

1000
01:40:43.803 --> 01:40:48.264
- Locktwaar danalora luatha danu...
- Oh. Willow!

1001
01:40:48.391 --> 01:40:52.556
tuatha. tuatha. chnox danu.

1002
01:40:52.645 --> 01:40:56.764
Locktwaar danalora luatha danu tuath─

1003
01:40:56.857 --> 01:41:00.146
tuatha chnox... danu.

1004
01:41:12.915 --> 01:41:14.952
Raziel.

1005
01:41:24.552 --> 01:41:28.842
- Has it been so long?
- I'm sorry.

